                                                                                                                                                                    <p style='text-align: left;'>Summer Passholders will be contacted via email with information on pass pickup later this spring. 2021 hill access will require a booking in our reservation system. <strong><a data-id='1091188' data-title='Read more' href='https://www.winsport.ca/tickets-passes-and-rentals/seasons-passes-and-memberships/summer-pass/'>Read more</a></strong></p>
