                                                                                                                                                                    <span style='font-size:16px;'></span><span style='font-size: 16px;'><strong>IMPORTANT: WAIVERS REQUIRED AND LIABILITY NOTICE</strong></span>
                                                                                                                                                                    <p>Please find your ordered product below.</p>
                                                                                                                                                                    <p style='text-align: justify;'><strong><span style='font-size: 14px;'></span></strong></p>
                                                                                                                                                                    <p style='text-align: justify;'><strong><span style='font-size: 14px;'></span></strong></p>
