                                                                                                                                                                    <p style='text-align: left;'><span style='font-size: 10px;'></span><span style='font-size: 10px;'><strong><u>TERM OF CONTRACT:</u><br /> IMPORTANT: LIABILITY NOTICE</strong><br /> Your WinSport ticket purchase is subject to WinSport&rsquo;s Exclusion of Liability and Assumption of Risk Notice,&nbsp;<strong>which will affect your legal rights including the right to sue for negligence, breach of contract or breach of the Occupiers&rsquo; Liability Act or to claim compensation following an accident.&nbsp;<a data-id='1091189' data-title='PLEASE READ THIS NOTICE CAREFULLY! ' href='https://www.winsport.ca/assets/10518_Winter-Preparedness_20-21_ExlusionOfLiability-11.13.20_8.5x11.jpg' target='_blank'>PLEASE READ THIS NOTICE CAREFULLY!</a></strong></span></p>
                                                                                                                                                                    <p style='text-align: left;'><span style='font-size: 14px;'></span></p>
                                                                                                                                                                    <p style='text-align: left;'><span style='font-size: 14px;'><strong>Programs</strong></span></p>
                                                                                                                                                                    <p style='text-align: left;'><span style='font-size: 10px;'>Participation in any WinSport camp, program, or lesson (the &ldquo;Program&rdquo;) is subject to completion of WinSport&rsquo;s Release of Liability, Waiver of Claims, Assumption of Risks and Indemnity Agreements (the &ldquo;Waivers&rdquo;) by each participant or their parent/legal guardian prior to the first day of the Program. <strong>PLEASE READ THESE WAIVERS CAREFULLY! By signing, you will waive or give up certain legal rights including the right to sue for negligence, breach of contract, or breach of the Occupiers&rsquo; Liability Act or claim compensation following an accident.</strong> In the event the Waivers are not completed, participation in the Program shall not be permitted and a refund will be provided. </span></p>
                                                                                                                                                                    <p style='text-align: left;'><span style='font-size: 14px;'><strong>WinSport Season Passes</strong></span></p>
                                                                                                                                                                    <p style='text-align: left;'><span style='font-size: 10px;'></span><span style='font-size:10px;'>A WinSport Season Pass (the &ldquo;Pass&rdquo;) is subject to the completion of WinSport&rsquo;s Release of Liability, Waiver of Claims, Assumption of Risks, and Indemnity Agreements (the &ldquo;Waivers&rdquo;) by each passholder or their parent or legal guardian (in the event of a minor) prior to the Pass being issued. <strong>PLEASE READ THESE WAIVERS CAREFULLY! By signing, you will waive or give up certain legal rights including the right to sue for negligence, breach of contract, or breach of the Occupiers&rsquo; Liability Act or claim compensation following an accident.</strong> In the event the Waivers are not completed, the Pass shall not be issued and a refund will be provided.</span><span style='font-size: 10px;'> </span></p>
                                                                                                                                                                    <p style='text-align: left;'><span style='font-size: 14px;'><strong>Rentals</strong></span></p>
                                                                                                                                                                    <p style='text-align: left;'><span style='font-size: 10px;'></span><span style='font-size:10px;'>Rental of WinSport Equipment (the &ldquo;Rental&rdquo;) is subject to completion of WinSport&rsquo;s Release of Liability, Waiver of Claims, Assumption of Risks and Indemnity Agreements (the &ldquo;Waivers&rdquo;) by the equipment user or their parent/legal guardian prior to the first day of the Rental. <strong>PLEASE READ THESE WAIVERS CAREFULLY! By signing, you will waive or give up certain legal rights including the right to sue for negligence, breach of contract, or breach of the Occupiers&rsquo; Liability Act or claim compensation following an accident.</strong> In the event the Waivers are not completed, the rental shall not be permitted and a refund will be provided.</span></p>
                                                                                                                                                                    <p style='margin: 1em 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left;'>The Waivers can be viewed and completed by clicking on the link(s) below.</p>
